{"type": "article", "id": 24774, "title": "从细条纹到牛仔夹克，来看新一季快时尚又给了什么诱惑", "description": "还包括一些价位不算太高的品牌。", "date": "2016-04-01T07:09:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3677, "name": "衬衫"}, {"id": 22864, "name": "春季"}, {"id": 1690, "name": "流行"}, {"id": 7722, "name": "条纹"}, {"id": 25682, "name": "睡衣"}, {"id": 8761, "name": "丝绸"}, {"id": 11718, "name": "印花"}, {"id": 35, "name": "复古"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 14878, "name": "Reformation"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 11071, "name": "Forever21"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702113433oldNZiSTC7JDh8Yj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">对于大多数人来说，可能完全不会 care 秀场上流行什么和下一季的趋势，总觉得光怪陆离与日常的穿着有些遥远；有的因为价格等因素也只是保持观望。还有的人在换季时分总会异常焦灼，不知道买哪些新衣服来跟上四季更替的脚步。</p>\n<p class=\"\">那么不妨看一看快时尚们<a href=\"http://www.zara.com/hk/en/editorials/woman-the-spring-report-c816020.html\">最近发布的春季潮流趋势</a>，或许有些新购物灵感。</p>\n<h2>春季要清新：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113419YjvAsHzwn2OqceVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Zara </p>\n<p class=\"\">春天这种万物复苏的季节，最适合穿清新的衬衫了，浅色衬衫不管是单穿、内搭都很亮眼，简约、干练、清纯等等优点集于一身。可以选择细节处比较特别的设计，比如在袖口、领口和下摆。而众多快时尚和一些随处可见到门店的品牌都会推出一些比较别致的衬衫。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113419Cvr6yMEIzi81Dtca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0px;\">左：&amp; Other Stories／右： Reformation</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><i></i></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113420M8a0rDuzwTkKJ25N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54271845\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021134208ILsbt25cR4WZdaT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64849624\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">右：H&amp;M</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p><i></i></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113421CSND9gJQ4V8d7Moy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">右：Style Mafia</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113421qMFsGT4RIChzDklg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://stylemafia.us/pages/style-mafia-lookbook#subscribe_popup\">左：Style Mafia</a> ／</span><i><a href=\"http://uk.sandro-paris.com/en/woman/tops-et-shirts/eva-top/E10411E.html?dwvar_E10411E_color=10\">右：Sandro</a></i></p>\n<p class=\"\">并且细条纹的衬衫也非常火，类似的条纹和面料也应用到各种裙装上：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113421ZSOiEm4gCb7s8P9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74899598\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">J.W.Anderson x NET-A-PORTER<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113422I8lHJxcnk0G2fwmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Victoria Beckham ／ <a href=\"http://uk.sandro-paris.com/en/woman/tops-et-shirts/cody-shirt/C10327E.html?dwvar_C10327E_color=10\">Sandro</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113422LPNhxVIsgA4u6JRB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ASOS ／<a href=\"https://www.thereformation.com/products/blanka-top-picasso\">Reformation</a></p>\n<h2>复古印花：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">最能代表春天的，当然要算上花朵，时尚品牌们到了春天大多都得出浪漫的印花面料。同时大片的印花总是带着复古的气息，和现代感十足的几何图案印花组合最妙，如同新旧的交替。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021134239BCafZwbe0pQGAUS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Zara</p>\n<p class=\"\"><i></i></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021134244vOjnlhTUAfGWy0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">右：Zara </p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113424at9slxeOIiYu1yX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/blumarine-spring-2016-campaign/\"> Blumarine</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113425VCgpmvjb53lP4KkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/floral-print-sun-dresses-shop/\">Express</a>  ／<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/for-love-lemons-spring-2016-lookbook/#jp-carousel-279799\">For Love Lemons</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">Reformation 本季推出了一整个花朵的系列，各式各样的款式<a href=\"https://www.thereformation.com/stories/spring-florals-collection\">可以点击这里查看</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113425IikCocuS8mTLPApy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76810073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113426GP5si2tKYCSvNdbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68509378\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113426iencGsEVjAH9uRMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68549172\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>慵懒气息：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">春天的午后，太阳一晒到处都暖洋洋的，流行已久的睡衣风潮此时更加应景。Zara 管这个叫“闺房”系列，那些柔软、丝滑的绸缎系列、轻薄的蕾丝系列、飘逸的阔型系列都可以纳入其中，看起来性感又不失优雅。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113427Qs2rMCGtWvyPlAkY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Zara</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113427ZwmEi8C2JWPf5eU3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">J. CREW<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113428IBHFSVxfTuoAYRnL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113428pGaWh6jfAqJeKsL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">H&amp;M  </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113429e34JTFvKBtgUQXa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71507607\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">左：Zara </p>\n<p class=\"\"><i></i></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113429fNuc9RHryvQXewEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70275792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113430xMy5PFGYLv17A2cg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6785361\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.thereformation.com/stories/slip-dresses\">Reformation</a></p>\n<h2>摇滚精神：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">柔软浪漫的讲完了，怎么能忽略最有型的牛仔和皮衣？摇滚范儿的行头厚度非常适合春秋两季。刚刚脱下臃肿的冬装，用这些非常修身塑形的衣服来迎接春天吧。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113430SmXVj47fgMJRUe8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Zara</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113431T3wbde5NHAR2CIBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Mango<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113431W4jVuQ2C1xeDETch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113432xg2qBdRXlzj4bAeV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68137255\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.thereformation.com/stories/tee-collection\">Reformation</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113432OUWGZT934INHYBha.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}